  "title": "[Entry-level] MARKETING TRAINEE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong><br />We are a growing organization specializing in events, marketing campaigns, and customer engagement, committed to developing talent through structured training and hands-on experience.</p><p><br /><strong>Job Description</strong><br />The Marketing Trainee will support marketing campaigns, events, and customer engagement activities while learning core marketing, communication, and branding skills.</p><p><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in executing marketing campaigns, events, and roadshows</p></li><li><p>Represent client brands and engage customers professionally</p></li><li><p>Support brand awareness and customer acquisition activities</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members to achieve campaign goals</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Interest in marketing and customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Team player</p></li><li><p>No experience required; training provided</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li><p>Structured training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Career progression opportunities</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives</p></li><li><p>Hands-on marketing experience</p></li><li><p>Supportive team culture</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Career Level:</strong> Entry Level / Fresh Graduates / Career Switchers<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time</p><p><strong>Interested candidates are welcome to apply.</strong></p>",
